text.section:
Such release may be delivered to any of the following:
Any person specified for such purpose in the instrument creating the power;
Any trustee of the property to which the power relates;
Any person, other than the donee of the power, who could be adversely affected by an exercise of the power; or
The recorder of deeds of the county in which the donee of the power resides or has a place of business, or in which the deed, will or other instrument creating the power is recorded.
